320528.summary: Dr. Bappaditya Sarkar is an Orthopedics, Trauma and Minimally invasive Surgeon and has been practicing for last 18 years. He is an expert Trauma and Emergency surgeon and performs a range of Minimally invasive surgeries too. Some of the areas that he is specialized are surgeries for Fractures and limb surgeries, arthritis treatment and Keyhole surgeries. Dr. Sarkar operates at multiple clinics in Kolkata, providing world-class treatment at cost-effective prices. Being an experienced doctor, his fellows and counterparts often approach him for discussing complicated issues. Whenever he operates upon a patient, he makes sure all the procedures are aptly followed leaving no stone unturned to give the possible medical service.  The doctor has done his MBBS from Calcutta National Medical College in the year 2002. He has pursued his diploma in orthopedics in the year 2009 and has undergone MS degree in Surgery in the year 2012. All the qualifications are from Calcutta National Medical College.   The doctor has undertaken a special course in Fellowship in Minimal Access Surgery from IPGMER in the year 2016. He had an excellent academic career and has been a great reputed professional among his peer group.

686847.summary: Dr. Sanjoy Bagchi is a Trauma Surgeon and Orthopaedician presently practices at NH Narayana Multispeciality Hospital (Kolkata). He accomplished his MBBS and MS (Ortho) from Calcutta Medical College. He served more than 15 years, during the span he solved many complicated cases, successfully and precisely.   Dr. Bagchi is a prominent Trauma Surgeon known for his expertise in treating acute physical injuries on an emergency basis and during this trauma surgery, he encompasses treatment of the most severe, life-threatening, penetrating and blunt force injuries. Moreover, he performs all surgical procedures that are necessary on an immediate basis, as well as for follow-up surgery.    Other than that, Dr. Bagchi treats the injuries of the musculoskeletal system and takes care of bones, joints, ligaments, tendons, muscles and nerves. Dr. Bagchi is also specialized in arthroscopy surgery of knee ligaments like ACL repair, PCL repair, and meniscus arthroscopic surgery.

687660.summary: Dr. Manoj Kumar Khemani is a highly qualified and experienced Orthopaedic surgeon and an accomplished clinician. He has an experience of treating more than 8000 patients. He is an alumnus of B. S. Medical College, Calcutta University and received his specialist training from the prestigious Dr. D. Y. Patil Medical College, Pune. He completed his Mch. Ortho degree from the University of Seychelles and Advanced trauma life support course from AIIMS.  He has rich expertise in Joint Replacement surgeries, Complex Trauma, Sports and Spinal injuries. He also specializes in General and Elderly orthopedics. He has a special interest in osteoporosis and related complications.  Dr. Manoj Kumar Khemani is a member of the Indian Medical Association Indian Orthopedics Association and West Bengal Orthopaedic Association. He is also a life member of Trauma Society of India, Indian Arthroscopy Society & West Bengal Arthroplasty Society. He works from his clinic Healing Touch in Bangor Avenue. He is fully dedicated to his patients.

742896.summary: Meet Dr. Gautam Gupta, a highly respected orthopedic surgeon with over 14 years of specialized experience. Dr. Gupta is renowned for his expertise in advanced procedures including knee and hip replacements, ligament injuries, sports trauma, and fractures. Having received extensive international training in the Netherlands and Germany, Dr. Gupta brings a global perspective to his practice. Currently serving as a Consultant Orthopedic Surgeon in Kolkata, Dr. Gupta is dedicated to providing compassionate and high-quality orthopedic care to each patient.  Trust Dr. Gautam Gupta to create personalized treatment plans tailored to your orthopedic needs, ensuring optimal outcomes and a path towards better orthopedic health. 763820.summary: To serve the humanity is main motto upto my ability and credibility. Spreading love and gratitude. Currently attached to Apollo Gleneagles Hospital, Spandan Hospital, Kolkata.
